data.description: Experience the epitome of comfortable and stylish living in this newly listed 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home located in the heart of Tracy. Recently painted inside, this residence exudes freshness and modernity. The property is equipped with solar panels, not only enhancing its eco-friendliness but also significantly reducing your energy bills. Step outside into your own backyard paradise featuring a delightful built-in pool, perfect for warm summer days and outdoor gatherings. Inside, the open concept layout seamlessly connects the well-appointed kitchen with the family room. The separate dining area and living room makes it ideal for both daily living and entertaining. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home is in close proximity to schools, parks, shopping centers, and freeway access, making it an ideal family home. Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property yours!
